The UK Research Office is the European office of its sponsoring organisations, the UK Research Councils, and subscribing institutions (in the main UK HEIs). UKRO's mission is to maximise UK engagement in EU-funded research, innovation and higher education activities. www.ukro.ac.uk/&#xd;
